    <description>
![Screenshot of Ultimate Settings Panel](https://fsdn.com/con/app/proj/ultimatesettingspanelpro/screenshots/win7.PNG)

###Windows based all in one settings and configuration solution

An all in one settings and configuration solution for a multitude of configuration options in Windows, Office, Powershell and popular internet browsers. The latest release now has 15 different configuration tabs including Windows 10 and a total of 295 configuration items spanning across all versions of Windows, Powershell, Outlook, Server Administration, Google Chrome, Firefox, Internet Explorer and even some telnet tricks!

One of the great features of Ultimate Settings Panel is the ability to have a massive range of computing options all in one easy to use utility.

New in version 6.1 is the ability to now change your theme and styles colors within the utility and it will automatically save these settings as you go. This means that when you next load the utility, it will load in your previously set theme and colors! This has been our most requested addition to Ultimate Settings Panel and we are now delighted to be able to bring this to you.

###Features
* Windows Admin Tab
* General Admin Tab
* Windows 10 Admin Tab
* Outlook Admin Tab
* Server Admin Tab
* Windows 8 Tab
* Google Chrome Tab
* Internet Explorer Tab
* Firefox Tab
* Advanced Tab
* Windows 7, 8.1 and 10 Compatibility
* Windows 7 Tab
* Theme and Colour Scheme Changer
* CPU Information
* RAM Information
* Battery Information

**[PACKAGE NOTES](https://github.com/bcurran3/ChocolateyPackages/blob/master/ultimate-settings-panel/readme.md)**
